[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Providing women with free, confidential legal advice 
[normal]by specialist women solicitors and barristers.
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Enabling women to understand and benefit from their legal rights through accessible and timely publications and training.
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Campaigning to ensure that women’s voices are heard and law and policy meets all 
[normal]women’s needs.
